<subSubSection pageId="50" pageNumber="495" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageId="50" pageNumber="495">
Morphologically and ecologically nearest to 
<taxonomicName authority="Legrand, 1982" authorityName="Legrand" authorityYear="1982" box="[676,1036,450,477]" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Aciagrion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="balachowskyi">
<emphasis box="[676,862,450,477]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="495">
A. 
<misspelling pageNumber="495" type="misspelled">balachowskyi</misspelling>
</emphasis>
Legrand, 
<number box="[979,1036,450,476]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="1982.0">1982</number>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Pinhey, 1964" authorityName="Pinhey" authorityYear="1964" box="[212,533,487,514]" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Aciagrion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nodosum">
<emphasis box="[212,352,487,514]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="495">
A. 
<misspelling pageNumber="495" type="misspelled">nodosum</misspelling>
</emphasis>
(Pinhey, 
<number box="[467,525,487,514]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="1964.0">1964</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
but genetically nearer 
<taxonomicName authority="Sjostedt, 1909" authorityName="Sjostedt" authorityYear="1909" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Aciagrion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gracile">
<emphasis box="[808,918,487,514]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="495">A. gracile</emphasis>
(Sjöstedt, 
<number box="[159,217,524,551]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="1909.0">1909</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
and treated as a distinct species on account of its unique male appendages by Dijkstra &amp; Clausnitzer (
<number box="[633,695,562,588]" pageId="50" pageNumber="495" value="2014.0">2014</number>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
